One thing I've realized I hate is *Drum Roll* Family Circus. You know, the little comic strip that has Jeffy, Dotty, and some other kid thats name ends with a "Y" and their mismatched adventures in the life of a child who is raised by a devote christian family. Ooooo, what mischief he'll get themselves into!

WOW DOTTY!!! Looks like you are a talented little one huh! Ya see this is the kinda shit that pisses me off! this shit is so damn stupid. If my kid ever said that they would get a nice backhand for damn sure! Does Dotty realize no one really gives a shit that she can make scrambled eggs without looking at the "Menu", and what the hell is "Mommy" doing while all this is going on? Is she opening the liquor cabinet? And why the hell is she wearing sneakers while in a nightgown? Is that a spoon she's holding? Nevermind lets go to the next comic

TADPOLES!?!?! What the hell is Dotty's fucking problem? I mean come on, tadpoles? Why is there a gift shop just randomly there? Whats "Mommy" doing this time? Does this woman ever watch her kids? She sure as hell doesn't dress them. Pink and Black? Who the hell thinks thats a decent color scheme? Is anyone besides me worried about why the Native Americans put a cross fusion between Bozo the clown and the coneheads on top of their totempoles, I mean "Tadpoles"? Is that a Quacker on the top of the other one?

Well it looks like Dotty doesn't like feminisim. Dotty are you trying to say a woman's place is in the kitchen? Also isn't this comic from 2000? 2002? Can you even find a big screen TV that is in black and white? Does Dotty have anyother cloths? Same old Pink and Black mismatched outfit.

Ok, this next one just threw me through a loop, what is going on?

Is "Daddy" coming on to the kids? Whats happening here?

Well at least there is someone who hate Family Circus too

http://www.avalon.net/~matrix/fc/index.html

Hilarious, trust me. Sex, Booze, Drugs, Gambling, Dead Things, and Family Circus

I'm gonna sound like I have no life, but if you were in my shoes you'd understand.... Most of you will watch cable tonight. Tonight there is no cable for Michael. Thats right kiddies, cable has left the DuBois/Puleo house. DAMN IT! Mom why? Cause its tooooo expensive? BULL SHIT!!! Now I have 15 channels!!! 15!... hold on *turns on tv* I'm gonna names all my channels (and rank them) for ya

Ch2 - ABC - Eh

Ch3 - Fox - Some salvation in this hell hole

Ch4 - PAX - The worst network EVER!!!

Ch5 - TVBCC - BCC has a channel? Why?

Ch6 - WKGM - Don't really know about this one.

Ch7 -WFTV - Don't really know about this one.

Ch8 - WB - Home of great shows such as 7th Heaven.

Ch9 - UPN.... I think it's got two images on top of each other. One is a Winsor Pilaties infomercial, and the other is a... football game? - Well clearly this is some quality programing

Ch10 - Zap It (Info Channel) - YAY!!! Now I can look at all the shows that look good, but I can't watch. THANKS ASSHOLE!!!!

Ch14 - No idea but some gospel channel - I doubt I'll ever watch this crap.

Ch16 - UPN? uhhh I thought ch9 was UPN?- I may watch this I duno, prolly more crappy programing

Ch17 - Spanish channel #1 - Pretty funnyif you like watching thing where you have no idea whats going on. They even have a talk show with the following in the audience: Evil Luchador, Werewolf, Alien With Baby, Girl with Huge Prostetic Ears, Witch, Vampire, and Guy in aWannabe Darth Vader Suit. - I have one word to say to this. In the words of my good friend Phil "WOWZA!" Great programing.

Ch18 - Spanish channel #2 WTF!? Why do we need two? - Mucho muy crappy programar!

Ch19 - BSPTV - Some crappy new thing they put up.

Ch20 - PBS - As we all know this is the second crappiest channel inthe world.

Ch21 - Wannabe PBS - This is yet another really gay network.

Ch22 - WTGL - I duno it's got alot of Informercials

Ch98 - CSPAN2 (No I didn't skip from 22 to 98 there is nothing in the middle) - What ever happend to CSPAN #1?

Ch99 - Government Access? - Why is thiseven a channel?

Yea thats what I have to watch now. It BLOWS!!!! So yea lots and lots of boredom and static channel surfing comming my way. When I get a job this is all gonna change though. I'm gonna pay for half the cable , and get a mini fridge, and get a Go-Cart ....... Well maybe not, but I'll get cable. And I'll be the one paying for it. See ya fuck with that one Ma!

Fluffy  1994 - 2002  He never saw the car

                                                                          (I miss Fluffy)

                     Under George Bush Fluffy died... Well not really, but George Bush sucks. Why did Kerry have to resign so late in the game!? Why couldn't he have resigned soon enough to let Mr. Ralph Nader lead America to a new era of prosperity? WHY!?!?! John Kerry you piss me off! But not as much as Georgy Boy here. George Bush is a flat out dumbass. Well the current song suits my mood. (Smashing Pumpkins - Bullet With Butterfly Wings), because no matter how much I want to change this country and no matter how much it pisses me off (Or how much RAGE I have), I'm just a kid (Rat) who can't do anything (In a Cage) yet.  Another thing is ..... um ..... ya know what George Bush sucks, he's the dumbest president we've ever had and he's making America look like a joke! Any one who can't see that must be blind. George Bush, you can take your victory and shove it! I'm glad in 4 years we won't have Mr. Dipshit here any more.

Well I know now what people mean when they say stop while you're ahead. I have been craving Heath ever since I got a small fun size bar for Halloween. Whats so fun about getting less candy? You can't do that with a liver transplant! Well Mr. Johnson, we couldn't get you a normal liver... so we gave you a fun sized one! Isn't that great! It's only about 1/3 the normal size so you'll prolly die, but isn't it cute! *shitty doctor smile*. Well lets get back to the subject at hand here. Heath is good. Addictive, just like crack. But too much of one thing can be bad. I had a flurry with Heath in it with Mary saturday. Oh man that was good! do you think I was satisfied? NO! So today I lounged about til about 4 andthen took a shower. Next I walked to K-Mart, and bought two Heath bites... they were 2 for $4. What if I had bought one and it had cost normal price, I'd be getting jipped! So I bought two. Not even half way home I was half way done with the first bag. Needless to say, I felt like I was gonna puke and shit out a nice big Heath bar of my own. Luckily I didn't. so now I've got some Heath I don't want to eat and a stomach ache that blows. One word to this: Heartburn, Indigestion, Nausea, Upset Stomach, DiahrheiaYAY Peptopismal!. Well maybe itwasn't one word, but it gets the point across. ...Shazam!

Well it appears I forgot something, and here it is: "I've found someone much better, and I'm happy. Happier than I ever was with you. I hope that you'll find someone who makes you half way as happy as Mary makes me."

Ahhh Jessica, What would I do without you? Hmm? I duno, but I'd prolly stop getting the feeling my balls are gonna ram themselves back into my stomach. Yeah I think thats the ticket there. Personally I am trying to get over the shit you did, and just let it by, but personally i think you're a bitch as well. Ya see my mood, I'm mimicing you! *Shitty Smile* Everytime you walk by me, I want to stick my foot out and watch  you smash your face in on the cement. I tryed being nice to you, and you spit it in my face, so ya can go fuck your self and die. You are a bitch and you treat almost everyone around you like shit. Anyone who's ever cared or tryed to care has been caught in the fury of your neverending period. (Honestly, when I went out with you it seemed every week ya had one. Ya might wanna get that checked out.) Your parents, your friends, your current and ex boyfriends. All of them can't escape your bitchiness. I wouldn't have such a problem with you if for one, you didn't give me dirty looks whenever you walked by me. Two if you would just go to hell already. Well thats all for now. Oh, and Jessica if you are reading this, I'd like to say one thing: "Have a nice day." *Shitty Forced Smile*
